OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man faces a prison
OL,7,Fsentence for creating a "handmade
OL,8,Fknuckleduster" out of a dog lead while
OL,9,Ftaunting and shouting abuse at police
OL,10,Fofficers during disorder in
OL,11,FSouthampton following the murder of
OL,12,FHenry Nowak, a court has heard.
OL,14,FDaniel Frost, of Northam Road,
OL,15,FSouthampton, has pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fviolent disorder and possessing a dog
OL,17,Flead with a metal carabiner attached.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
