OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FThe father-of-two was brought to
OL,7,FSouthampton Crown Court to be
OL,8,Fsentenced, but Judge William Mousley
OL,9,FKC adjourned the hearing for more
OL,10,Finformation on the scale of the
OL,11,Fdisorder.
OL,13,FMeanwhile a trial date has been set
OL,14,Ffor a 50-year-old man accused of
OL,15,Fassaulting a police officer during
OL,16,Fdisorder in Southampton following the
OL,17,Fdeath of Henry Nowak.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
