OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FMatt Styler, of Orange Grove, Gosport,
OL,7,Fhad pleaded not guilty to the charge
OL,8,Fduring a preliminary hearing at
OL,9,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court last
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,FJudge William Mousley KC, sitting at
OL,13,FSouthampton Crown Court on Monday,
OL,14,Fadjourned the case for a further plea
OL,15,Fand trial preparation hearing on June
OL,16,F26 with a trial date set for November
OL,17,F2, expected to last three days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
