OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FAt Southampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FMonday, a 41-year-old man pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to offences including violent
OL,9,Fdisorder following the protests.
OL,11,FLeon O'Leary admitted offences of
OL,12,Fviolent disorder, obstructing/
OL,13,Fresisting a constable and possessing
OL,14,Fan offensive weapon in a private
OL,15,Fplace, namely a sword in his bedroom.
OL,17,FO'Leary, who told the court he was of
OL,18,Fno fixed abode, will be sentenced at
OL,19,Fcrown court on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
