OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FHe is one of 20 people charged so far
OL,7,Fin the city over disorder on 2 June.
OL,9,FEleven Hampshire police officers and a
OL,10,Fpolice dog were injured as missiles
OL,11,Fincluding wheelie bins and chairs were
OL,12,Fthrown during protests organised in
OL,13,Fresponse to the murder of student
OL,14,FHenry Nowak.
OL,16,FEight others are expected to appear at
OL,17,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,18,FMonday charged with violent disorder,
OL,19,Faccording to Hampshire Police.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
