OL,3,CHenry Nowak: Further court appearances
OL,4,Cover Southampton disorder
OL,6,FThey are Benjamin Jones, 23, of
OL,7,FLocksley Road, Eastleigh; Tyler
OL,8,FBurley, 18, of Shakespeare Avenue,
OL,9,FSouthampton; Mariusz Szczyglo, 45, of
OL,10,FGrove Road, Southampton; Kamil Josef
OL,11,FKlonek, 33, of Lordswood Road,
OL,12,FSouthampton; Darren Medhurst, 36, of
OL,13,FCarnation Road, Southampton; Jordan
OL,14,FHambleton, 19, of Rollesbrook Gardens,
OL,15,FSouthampton; and Callum Darch, 27, of
OL,16,FSt Blaize Road, Romsey. Harley Haynes,
OL,17,F23, of Avenue Road in Southampton, has
OL,18,Falso been charged with affray, the
OL,19,Fforce said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
